<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        hr {
            border: 0;
            border-top: 2px solid #f1f1f1;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }
        .nav-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Welcome to about page</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <%- include('partials/nav'); %>
        <hr>
        <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Unde perferendis, animi nemo ex distinctio ad excepturi? Impedit aperiam labore culpa, quis earum, numquam debitis ab molestiae veritatis possimus accusamus nulla?
        </p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
